---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="About Us | Free Resume Builder" description="Learn about ResumeBuilder - our mission to help professionals create standout resumes for free.">
  <section style="padding:6rem 2rem 0;min-height:auto;display:block;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center">
    <div class="hero-split-content" style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center">
      <span class="eyebrow">About Us</span>
      <h1>Making Professional <span class="gradient-text">Resume Tools</span> Accessible to Everyone</h1>
      <p>Our mission is to remove barriers between talented professionals and their dream jobs with free, ATS-friendly resume tools.</p>
      <div class="hero-split-actions" style="justify-content:center">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Build My Resume</a>
        <a href="/resume-examples" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">View Examples</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <article>
        <p>ResumeBuilder is a free, online resume creation tool designed to help job seekers build professional, ATS-friendly resumes quickly and easily. Our mission is to remove barriers between talented professionals and their dream jobs.</p>

        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>ResumeBuilder was created to solve a simple problem: existing resume builders were either too expensive, too complicated, or produced resumes that Applicant Tracking Systems couldn't read. We believed everyone deserves access to a tool that creates beautiful, scannable resumes without requiring design skills or a subscription.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>100% Free</h3>
            <p>No hidden fees, no credit card required. All templates and features are completely free.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>ATS-Friendly</h3>
            <p>Our templates are optimized for Applicant Tracking Systems, ensuring your resume gets seen by recruiters.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Multiple Templates</h3>
            <p>Choose from Classic, Modern, Professional, and Creative designs to match your industry.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Privacy First</h3>
            <p>Your data stays on your device. We never store or share your personal information.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Accessibility</h3>
            <p>Making professional resume tools available to everyone, everywhere.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Simplicity</h3>
            <p>Removing complexity so you can focus on what matters — your content.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Quality</h3>
            <p>Ensuring every template meets professional standards and ATS requirements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Privacy</h3>
            <p>Protecting your data with a privacy-first, client-side architecture.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-sm section-tools">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Free Career Tools</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="tools-grid">
        <a href="/" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Resume Builder</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/ats-score" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>ATS Score</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/cover-letter" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Cover Letter</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/resume-examples" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Examples</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/templates" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Templates</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog" class="card tool-card card-hover">
          <span class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 016.5 17H20"/><path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 014 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 016.5 2z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <span>Blog</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="capture">
    <div class="capture-inner">
      <h3>Get Weekly Resume Tips</h3>
      <p>Join 10,000+ job seekers getting expert advice straight to their inbox.</p>
      <form class="capture-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault()">
        <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
        <button type="submit">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
      <p class="capture-note">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
